Sentencas: In this paper, electrical and electrochemical properties of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (LSCF) cathode have been studied.
Titulo: Preparation and investigation of electrical and electrochemical properties of lanthanum-based cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The sample is prepared by solid-state reaction method.
Titulo: Preparation and investigation of electrical and electrochemical properties of lanthanum-based cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The results of the X-ray diffraction have been analyzed by FullProf software and it has been found that LSCF phase has been formed.
Titulo: Preparation and investigation of electrical and electrochemical properties of lanthanum-based cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Resistance of the sample versus temperature in air atmosphere has been measured and the results show that, it decreases by increasing temperature.
Titulo: Preparation and investigation of electrical and electrochemical properties of lanthanum-based cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Activation energy for electrical conductivity has been calculated by fitting the Arrhenius plot with experimental data.
Titulo: Preparation and investigation of electrical and electrochemical properties of lanthanum-based cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Also, resistance of sample has been measured at the different temperature ranges and in the presence of Oxygen/Argon atmosphere.
Titulo: Preparation and investigation of electrical and electrochemical properties of lanthanum-based cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Using electrical relaxation technique and some approximations, ionic diffusion coefficient and activation energy for ionic conductivity have been calculated.
Titulo: Preparation and investigation of electrical and electrochemical properties of lanthanum-based cathode for solid oxide fuel cell
